## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Run application testing with `npm start` or the correct dev script.
2. Open Browser Developer Tools and enable "Device Toolbar" to simulate mobile resolutions (iPhone 12/13).
3. Verify the desktop sidebar is hidden and replaced by Bottom Nav and Top Mobile Header.
4. Verify routing using the Bottom Nav.
5. Navigate into an inner deep link (e.g. Daily view of a specific kid) and verify the Back/Home button returns cleanly to the parent view.
